= System Administration Tools =

Select the dummy MTA we want on i386

 * lsb-invalid-mta [i386]

Hardware related tools:

 * numactl   # LP: #1700826

Network related:

 * iptraf-ng
 * dnstracer
 * wakeonlan
 * iputils-arping

Log parsing and status gathering:

 * checksecurity
 * aide
 * smartmontools
 * logwatch
 * lsscsi
 * rsyslog-gnutls   # LP: #388605 - encrypt data sent by rsyslog for compliance
 * sysstat

Systems management:

 * freeipmi-tools
